<h2>Intro</h2>

<p>My frustration with Facebook is all about getting to the info I want, regardless of whether or not I'm following someone.</p>

<p>This demo app solves that by showing Chatter posts which match preconfigured keywords, more complex filters or common tags such as "#" and "@".<p>

<p>Keywords are single words of interest that combined with an OR.  The app queries using a 'LIKE' operation in the SOQL.</p>

<p>Filters have Filter Conditions.  A single filter might want posts with alpha and beta but not gamma.  Filter Conditions are combined with an AND and use either LIKE or NOT [field] LIKE.  Filters are combined with an OR.</p>

<h2>IMPORTANT</h2>

<p>You must configure keywords and filters before you will see results.</p>

<p>Tags are dynamic.</p>

<p>There is a custom settings object you can configure to your liking.

