<h2>Notes</h2>

<p>Why isn't this just a report?  Well, two reasons. First, I haven't seen any obvious reports on user feeds yet.  Second, this function combines multiple filters where each report would contain essentially a single filter.</p>

<p>Both Keyword and Filters are user specific.  You have to set up the particular filters you want per user.</p>

<p>Nothing will show up in the results page until you configure keywords or filters and have matching results.</p>

<p>Doesn't query comments.</p>

<p>Limits results to the first 100.</p>

